<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Vow Renewal & Tributes | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Anniversary Celebration vowsCss.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-section-annisasivows">
    <div class="hero-content-annisasivows">
      <h1 class="fade-slide">Vow Renewal & Heartfelt Tributes</h1>
      <p class="fade-slide">Celebrate enduring love and honor the hearts that shaped your journey</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Paragraph -->
  <section class="section-annisasivows fade-in-up-annisasivows vow-intro-annisasivows">
    <div class="intro-text-annisasivows">
      <p>
        Whether it's 5 years or 50, vow renewals are a beautiful reminder of your love story — 
        an intimate ceremony to honor the promises you’ve lived and the dreams you’re still building. 
        And through heartfelt tributes, we give thanks to those who’ve walked beside us — 
        mentors, family, friends — whose love helped shape ours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sample Vow -->
  <section class="section-annisasivows fade-in-up-annisasivows vow-example-annisasivows">
    <h2>Wedding renewal Vows</h2>
    <div class="vow-card-annisasivows">
      <p>
        “In every moment, you've been my heart's calm and spark. <br>
        Today, I promise once again to love, laugh, and grow with you — for all the tomorrows to come.”
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="vow-card-annisasivows">
      <p>
        “From the day I met you, you’ve been my heart’s home.<br>
        Today, I renew the promise to choose you — again and again — in every smile, every silence, every storm.<br>
        You are my always and forever.”
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="vow-card-annisasivows">
      <p>
        “It’s not just the big moments — it’s the way you make coffee, hold my hand, and laugh at my bad jokes.<br>
        I vow to keep loving you in the quiet and the chaos, in grocery aisles and starry nights.<br>
        You are my favorite part of every day.”
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="vow-card-annisasivows">
      <p>
        “We’ve grown, we’ve changed, and still…<br>
        You are the one I’d choose in every lifetime.<br>
        I vow to stand beside you — not just in love, but in friendship, in adventure, in every season of who we are.”
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="vow-card-annisasivows">
      <p>
       “I didn’t think it was possible to fall for you more — and then you smiled again.<br>
        I vow to keep discovering new ways to love you, new dreams to share, and new stories to write together.<br>
        I’m still falling — and I always will.”
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tribute Gallery -->
  <section class="section-annisasivows fade-in-up-annisasivows tribute-gallery-annisasivows">
    <h2>Heartfelt Tributes</h2>
    <div class="tribute-grid-annisasivows">
      <div class="tribute-card-annisasivows">
        <img src="/img/speech.jpeg" alt="Tribute of speech">
        <h3>“Words from the Heart”</h3>
        <p>Her love has always been my guide and my grounding.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tribute-card-annisasivows">
        <img src="/img/video clip.jpeg" alt="Tribute of video clip">
        <h3>“Chapters of Us”</h3>
        <p>The photos, clips, or messages from loved ones.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tribute-card-annisasivows">
        <img src="/img//song.jpeg" alt="Tribute of song">
        <h3>“Our Song, Our Story”</h3>
        <p>For showing lifetime of love from a song.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
